content: उत्क्षेप {%<ab>a.</ab>%} Throwing up, tossing. --पः {@--1@} Throwing or tossing up; पक्ष्मोत्क्षेप <ls>Me. 47.</ls> {@--2@} That which is thrown or tossed up; बिंदूत्क्षेपान् पिपासुः <ls>M. 2. 13.</ls> {@--3@} Sending, despatching. {@--4@} Throwing away, rejecting. {@--5@} Vomiting. {@--6@} The region above the temples (dual).
